  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Olympic is a popular and charming hotel with a welcoming atmosphere, offering excellent value accommodation in the centre of Montana and with easy access to the slopes. All the bedrooms have recently been renovated in a modern alpine-style.</p>
<p><strong>'Ski Inclusive' offer is now available for Winter 2016/17 bookings - valid for departures 23 Dec and from 7 Jan to end of season</strong> and includes: 7 nights accommodation on half board basis, 6-day whole area lift pass, 6-day ski/board and boot hire, Free equipment delivery and Free use of ski lockers at the lift - Book by 30 June 2016 for this very special offer, exclusive to Inghams.</p>]]></description>
